ansition in LaCoO$_3$ by temperature/hole doping is from an LS to an IS spin\nstate and the present work rules out the other possibilities reported in the\nliterature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Apr 2001 15:35:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
